The Kwale Union of Kenya Civil Servants yesterday said the medical scheme offered by the NHIF is &ldquo;useless&rdquo;. Led by Salim Mwachitu, the members said NHIF does not provide quality services.&ldquo;We are asked to buy medicine and pay for checkup in some hospitals,&rdquo; he said. Said Rajab said he had to pay Sh15,000 for his child t be admitted at Mewa hospital.